nteracting Green function is to be\nused instead of the non - interacting one. We, therefore, propose that the\nobtained expression may be used for the topological description of fractional\nquantum Hall effect.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 Mar 2023 22:05:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-30"}
