 show comparable correction performance with blipped-SMSlab.\n  Conclusion: The proposed model-based hybrid-space reconstruction can\nreconstruct blipped-SMSlab diffusion MRI successfully. Its extension to a joint\nreconstruction of the blip-up/down acquisition can correct EPI distortions and\nfurther reduce the g-factor penalty compared with the separate reconstruction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Mar 2023 03:55:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 31 Mar 2023 00:02:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-03"}
